text: Inna German (born 17 January 1983) is a Kazakhstani female volleyball player. She is a member of the Kazakhstan women's national volleyball team. She was part of the Kazakhstani national team at the 2014 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship in Italy. and at the 2016 Summer Olympics qualification.
